Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無限的時間將跳動停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們悄聲無息地燃燒著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有任何人注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界已經脫軌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被紅世之火所包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,---------------------------OP-----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:25.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そして　この空　赤く染めて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:31.63,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}また来る時　この一身で　進むだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:48.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}すれ違っていく‘人’も　紛れ失くした‘モノ’も
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:53.19,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつかは　消えゆく記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.39,0:00:59.54,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}熱く揺るがす‘強さ’　儚く揺れる‘弱さ’
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:04.80,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所詮　同じ結末
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.90,0:01:10.63,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そんな日常　紅霞を溶かし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:16.23,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}現れる陽　紅る世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:21.98,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}風になびかせ　線を引いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.11,0:01:27.61,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}流れるような髪先　敵を刺す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:33.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}振り斬った想い　漲る夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:38.52,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}すべては今　この手で　使命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:42.54,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}果たしてゆくだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:25.17,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}於是這片天空被染成紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:31.63,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再度來臨之際  唯以此身不斷向前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:48.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}擦肩而過之「人」  紛亂迷失之「物」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:53.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}終將成為  消失的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.39,0:00:59.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}熱烈震撼的「堅強」  虛無飄渺的「脆弱」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:04.80,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}終究是  同一結局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.90,0:01:10.63,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如此平凡  溶化於晚霞之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:16.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}升起的太陽  通紅的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:21.98,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}隨風飄揚  勾畫路線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.11,0:01:27.61,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}宛如飄揚的髮梢  刺向敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:33.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}揮刀斬斷的思念  瀰漫夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:42.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}一切都於此刻  僅以這雙手達成使命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,---------------------------ED-----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:59.52,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}夜明け生まれ来るものよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.88,0:23:04.26,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}決して見失わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.73,0:23:09.12,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You are you　少女よ　今こそ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.53,0:23:15.47,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}振りほどき立ちあがれ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.28,0:23:36.33,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}胸の傷を隠したまま　風を切り進む君を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:41.53,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ただ見守る術など何もない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:50.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}その瞳はずっと先の　自分を探しているの?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.38,0:23:58.27,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}でも聞こえるよ　深い悲しみの鼓動が叫んでる!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.77,0:24:03.05,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm just　夜明け前の暗闇が
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.07,0:24:06.41,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一生を運命づける
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.41,0:24:09.77,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大丈夫　少女よ　今こそ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.77,0:24:15.37,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}悔やみ恥じることはない　Far way…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.37,0:24:22.97,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}十字を背負い　死ぬ気で炎を駆けろ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:59.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}拂曉降生的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.88,0:23:04.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}決不可迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.73,0:23:09.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You are you  少女啊  就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.53,0:23:15.47,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}掙開手站起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.28,0:23:36.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}隱藏著胸口的傷痕  破風前進的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:41.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}除了注視  我別無他法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:50.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你那瞳孔是否正在  探尋著前方的自我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.38,0:23:58.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不過我能夠聽見  你那深情悲戚的心正在吶喊著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.77,0:24:03.05,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm just  拂曉前的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.07,0:24:06.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}將此一生付為命運
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.41,0:24:09.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}沒事的  少女啊  就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.77,0:24:15.37,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}沒什麼好懊悔羞愧的  Far way…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.37,0:24:22.97,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}背負著十字架  以死的覺悟向著火焰疾走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:44.86,Optitle,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(315,240)}戀愛和欲望的游泳池畔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在與被稱為悼詞朗誦者的火霧戰士的激烈戰鬥中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.89,0:01:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜得到了新的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勝利然後分別
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但當時的我卻沒能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜新的戰鬥快要逼近城市了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別追銀了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個光追是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微留情點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己提出的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是這麼說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是偶然的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊的  肯定不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱  真的好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼一大早就這麼熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.18,0:02:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天熱是理所當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.98,0:02:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你現在懶得很啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算堅持每天早上的鍛煉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻完全沒有進步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也該考慮才能的成分嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  已經留好退路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想說的是  現階段裡  別用這種話來逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說起才能的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在能更好行動的基礎上才談的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再認真點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等  等一下啊  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了  池
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你了  池同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,池  你在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲  因為父親工作的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到大量御崎水上樂園的門票
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就發給班上的同學了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御崎水上樂園就是那個最近才開張的「啊哈」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天啊  泳衣啊  御崎水上樂園  啊哈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  我想大家會不會很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是池
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給  平井同學也有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  泳衣打算怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天去買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又一副懶懶的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得拿到了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明後天就
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹  幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上課之前  對老師就有意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,領帶太花俏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:04:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很新潮啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛  悠二那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對著一張票傻笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太懶了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遊樂設施的入場券嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道什麼原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類很喜歡玩水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣說來也很合乎情理了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這樣  心情和臉都太懶了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才沒進步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  亞拉斯托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水上樂園是不是和浴室一樣很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  去屋頂吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:06:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜還是沒在中午前回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  平井同學去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鄰鎮的麵包店
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛤？為什麼又
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  可能中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然蜜瓜包重要的就是這種既香脆又鬆軟的口感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  這個  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問  不介意的話大家一起吃便當好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾這樣也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多人在一起邊吃邊開心地聊天比較有滋味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  坂井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什  什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  便當總是吃便利商店的飯糰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛  老媽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男孩子如果一日三餐都吃母親親手做的飯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能出人投地了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的話不對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是邀請坂井去水上樂園嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可  可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  有事想商量下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得池同學的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期天大家一起去水上樂園如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緒方同學  大家是指
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  全班的話好像太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡的人和那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊兩人怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無所謂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井也沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平井同學也沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班級裡的女主角不來的話就不能開始啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼關係  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好是好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期天10點在水上樂園集合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣  你們可別遲到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆從以前開始就老是遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別隨便決定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緒方  抱歉啊  有些事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像做了對不起緒方的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說週末無論如何都要把瑪裘莉小姐  帶到外面去的可是你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天以來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐天天在房子裡喝的爛醉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再不帶她去哪玩玩的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體就會壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來  兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是這窩囊的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爛醉的睡美人——瑪裘莉·頓喲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  早安  歡迎回來  又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件泳衣如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  也不那麼花俏  這種挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緒  緒方同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緒方同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緒方同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都和男孩子一起去游泳池了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛穿老土的泳衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試穿這個之前衣服就交我保管了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛情愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來  快穿快穿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再  再等會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好是好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就快讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緒方同學  你就饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是穿這個看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說了普通的一件頭就行了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.03,0:11:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給  小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳衣給你買來了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和大家一起去游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還穿學校的泳衣也太那個了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太那個了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是說能穿上在學校不能穿的  可愛泳衣的意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就試穿看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡好好等著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你難道不知道學習這種東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:12:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說了是誤會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附近有這個的話夏天可算是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中和佐藤好像真的不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電話也一直沒人接
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們倆怎麼都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們5個開心的玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水中情侶騎馬戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男女一組進行水中騎馬戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優勝組的獎品是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看到夜景的餐廳的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豪華晚餐免費招待券和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手製麵包任吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手製麵包任吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看到夜景的餐廳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為你的眼眸乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹  乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺有意思的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正下午才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,參加試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我參加
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就這樣決定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然少個男士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個等下再考慮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同學她們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要著急不要著急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來是緣和一美的泳衣時裝秀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是平井小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有請
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來是吉田小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有請
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緒  緒方同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  別管那麼多  快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地獄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐  別這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不偶爾外出的話身體可會壞掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的情況出門反而對身體不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許是這樣也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,榮太  那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪裘莉小姐  真的要現在進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然囉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠避暑的只有這裡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不如改明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的日子有些不合適
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悼詞朗誦者來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？悼詞的？那個人來這了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然感覺不到殺氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到兩個火霧戰士都來這個游泳池悠閒地玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就有點想笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去下小賣部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還是來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐一說出口就不聽別人的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.64,0:15:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但可能不太妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一碰到緒方她們的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該說什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那麼多人在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能那麼容易就碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  你們倆在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緒方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  這是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是叫他們去買個酒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啟作和榮太都不知道在搞什麼飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈  對你粗暴的喝酒方式終於忍受不了了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈  好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒絕了我的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼還會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道  雖然不太清楚  大概是三角關係之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  果然只是來玩的囉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在可沒心情和你幹架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想打的話找別人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在水邊喝點酒再睡一覺的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.01,0:16:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悼詞朗誦者也就滿足囉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悼詞朗誦者作為火霧戰士也到頭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  但對我們來說無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  昨天說不去是為了嚇大家一跳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們想簡單地說去太無趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  只是在這裡突然出現熱鬧一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧  田中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連我也不告訴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話會參加騎馬戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎馬戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶子連著的兩人就組隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多出來的人就專心加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  大姐可是一直在等著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.07,0:17:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起瑪裘莉小姐的事曝光來得要好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我放手囉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於來到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御崎水上樂園特產
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水中情侶騎馬戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,規則很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搶到最多頭巾的隊伍就是優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  頭巾被奪走或是兩人分開就為失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,池那傢伙跑哪去上廁所了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說會好好加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在規定時間內搶到最多頭巾的情侶將會得到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看得到夜景的餐廳的晚餐和豪華獎品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和坂井同學在能看到夜景的餐廳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和坂井同學在能看到夜景的餐廳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贏了的話蜜瓜包任吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贏了的話蜜瓜包任吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了嗎  田中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是靠你的機動力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那麼緊張的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放鬆點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  熱鬧激烈的水中騎馬戰開幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:18:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,限定時間為3分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認識的互相爭奪也不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去搶別人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一美也挺不賴的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎馬戰果然還是要靠頭腦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像也有不靠頭腦都很厲害的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  還要來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.09,0:19:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平井同學好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是佐藤比較厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不用勉強和他們打了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.64,0:20:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間所剩無幾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下來的情侶也越來越少
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同學  好不容易留下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣等到時間結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不能優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定能拿到點什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能像這樣待在坂井同學身邊就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔唷  平井組行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  逃吧  吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.01,0:20:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要追啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.18,0:20:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打敗我們也沒意義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是鍛煉的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能那樣的投機  真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同學  再把身體俯低些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  再快點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就  就算這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二  給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小緣  莫非是因為我和坂井同學黏在一起才發火的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再追近些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經是極限
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學  來了  來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二  覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優勝者是撿到便宜的岡田組
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來岡田老師也來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.01,0:21:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但  這也算嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人是他太太嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  幹嘛要追上來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.09,0:21:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:21:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.09,0:21:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且夏娜也總是總是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年  你也喝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.60,0:22:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年不能喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真頭痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這人到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道大家怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.20,0:22:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐  真抱歉把你丟一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.33,0:22:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.46,0:22:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像把奇怪的東西當枕頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.65,0:22:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脖子好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.90,0:22:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那今天就在這裡解散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.51,0:22:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期一學校再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.41,0:22:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底為什麼要追來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.06,0:24:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法用語言表達的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.46,0:24:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜獨自一人揮舞著劍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.20,0:24:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瀰漫著磷子的慘叫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.87,0:24:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後城市裡出現了新的紅世之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.12,0:24:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回  糾纏的思念
